data.description: This nearly new and lightly lived in contemporary craftsman style home features upgraded materials and finishes, including metal roofing, decorative rock on the exterior, plywood sheathing, granite counters throughout the home and double sinks in the master bedroom. As you enter the home through the solid wood entry door, you are greeted by a vaulted ceiling home with an open floor plan and a spacious kitchen with custom alder cabinets, stainless steel appliances, an expansive center island and large side-by-side refrigerator. LVP flooring is in the living spaces and the bedrooms are carpeted. The laundry room is spacious and features granite counters and an abundance of cabinets. the energy efficient ductless heating/cooling system helps control your electric usage. There is a low maintenance landscaped yard in the front with a covered front deck and a rear deck with Trex decking and privacy fencing.
